'''Reclamation Services, Inc.''' ('''RSI''') was a [[Tal'cara]]-based corporation that specialized in smelting and incineration. Owned by [[Ukert]], the company recycled waste materials and turned them into usable forms, such as metals and plastics.<ref name="GR">''{{WEGCite|story=Garbage Run|book=Shadows of the Empire Planets Guide}}''</ref>

